name: Let the wild stay wild
description:
“Promise to stay wild with me. We’ll seek and return and stay and find beauty and the extraordinary in all the space we can claim. We’ll know how to live. How to breathe magic into the mundane.”- Victoria Erickson

This piece is based on my 2014 papercut works, I added some digital editing and animation.

Music by me
Mixing mastering at Sembungan Open Air Studio with Ikbal Lubys

Special thanks to Rudi Hermawan, Ikbal Lubys and Gilang Kusuma for helping me.
